title: Little Devil Teemo Icon from doom bots still haven't receive

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: I've played the teemoing a couple of times as soon as it released and i played with 2 friends of mine and we eventually won. But today my friend got the icon but i haven't yet. I also played again today just to make sure i would get the icon sometime next week, but im still curious would i get sometime this week even tho my friends have gotten them.

replies.body: We're sending these out over time and the last date to receive them are on November 17th. If you don't have anything by midnight on the 17th, go ahead and submit a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) and we'll help you out.
